&lt;b&gt;Eulogy Ability Points&lt;/b&gt;

For the Eulogy, Medenia class Aislings will receive ability points in addition to the standard experience points when performing the Eulogy. The amount of points, like experience, will be based on the amount of Eulogies the Aisling has performed with one specific priest of the Trinity.

1x (1st time performing Eulogy) 25,000 ability points
2x 50,000 ability points
3x 100,000 ability points
4x 175,000 ability points
5x 250,000 ability points
6x 350,000 ability points
7x 475,000 ability points
8x 600,000 ability points
9x 800,000 ability points
10x+ 1,000,000 ability points 

((Eulogy will start on Friday, November 13th and end on November 30th.))</Content>
